    <h3><a href="/node/17#comment-96" class="active">Demonstrate it using a SIP phone in peer-to-peer mode</a></h3>

    <div class="content">
      <p>As an extension to this, a demonstration using an AIR-based complete SIP phone supporting Speex/G.711 audio, H.264 video, instant messaging and presence, as well as NG911 calling will be great.</p>
          </div>
  </div>

