    <h3><a href="/node/17#comment-31" class="active">P2P simulator</a></h3>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Build a peer-to-peer network simulator in Python that implements various structured and unstructured algorithms. Related work includes p2psim, oversim and peersim. This project will build several modules to allow a developer to quickly put together an implementation of a P2P algorithm, view it graphically, and see the impact of various parameters. You should be able to support nodes behind NAT and firewall in your simulator, incorporate security and analyze the performance. Language: Python</p>
          </div>
  </div>

